entry.def: If a report or a rumour is unconfirmed, there is no definite proof as to whether it is true or not.

example.ex: There are unconfirmed reports of several small villages buried by mudslides.
example.tran: 据未经证实的报道说，几个小村庄被泥石流吞没了。
